info: Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: I have stayed at Sabrina’s place for 3 nights with my family. It was a pleasant experience, the accommodation was spacious and clean, the host clearly has a good choice in choosing her furnitures. She was responsive and welcoming. We enjoyed our stay at her accommodation and wish to come back to the same place in the future.
